    {
      "id": "/page/0/Text/5",
      "block_type": "Text",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"Text\">What this option emulates is the greedy strategy of liquidating a portfolioâ€”the best performing stocks are sold first. Since this is a derivative product, Himalayan options may offer regulatory and tax benefits compared to actual holding of a portfolio.</p>",
