    {
      "id": "/page/1/Text/4",
      "block_type": "Text",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"Text\" class=\"has-continuation\">Assets with low correlation, on the other hand, become more disperse as time passes. Since the expected sum of assets at termination of the option is independent of correlation, removing the best</p>",
      "page": 171,
      "polygon": [
        [
          79.34765625,
          352.7471008300781
